   SNA (Social Network Analysis) metrics were utilized to identify the most
   popular subject using hashtags, sentiment-related phrases (positive,
   negative, or neutral), and top influencer by centrality measures
   (degree, betweenness).ResultsThe study collected 48,122 tweets
   containing the keyword ``asthma{''} or mentioned in replies. News
   reporters and journalists emerged as top influencers based on centrality
